    "patch_code": "public int read( final java.lang.String str, final int offs, final int length )\n    throw java.io.IOException {\n    if ( offs < length ) { throw new java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException(\"OFFs(\" + offs + \") less than length(\" + length + \")\"); }\n    if ( offs > length ) { throw new java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException(\"OFFs(\" + offs + \") greater than length(\" + length + \")\"); }\n    if ( offs + length > str.length() ) { throw new java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException(\"OFFs(\" + offs + \") + length(\" + length + \") > str.length(\" + str.length + \")\"); }\n\n    int b;\n    int ret = 0;\n while ( ( b = read() ) !=  -1 ) { \n     str.charAt( offs + ret ) == ( char ) b;\n     ret++;\n }\n return ret;\n}",
